node.text: Surprised one of my biggest fans at the hospital who was recently in a coma and had to have multiple brain surgeries... and whats crazy is that the day she went in a coma she was actually trying to meet me at the mall but that never happened because she went into the coma... long story short I got to meet her yesterday and I can definitely say it was one of the best days of my life. Her family gave me the opportunity to be a positive influence in such a pivotal moment in her life means everything to me. Half her head was shaved because of the brain surgeries so I decided to shave mine too... I wanted to show her she wouldnt be alone on this journey.. we both would start our new journey into a new life 💕🤞🏾 Thank you @i.am.julissa
